        <p id="Par55">This clearly shows that the use of the moving window provides smoother evaluations, thanks to the contribution of the neighbour bases, maintaining robustness in the identification of the HOT zones (most HOT zones overlap with the ones found with <inline-formula id="IEq22"><alternatives><tex-math id="M49">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
